---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Candidates - BOSS Consult | Find Your Next Tech Role"
  description="Looking for your next career move? BOSS Consult offers free CV review, interview preparation, and career coaching to help you land your dream tech role."
>
  <main class="pt-24">
    <section class="bg-brand-dark text-white py-20 lg:py-28">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Looking for Your Next Career Move?</h1>
        <p class="text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed mb-8">We are dedicated to helping you find the perfect tech role. From CV optimisation to interview coaching and beyond, BOSS Consult supports you at every stage of your career journey — completely free of charge.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-3 bg-brand-accent hover:bg-brand-accent-light text-white font-semibold rounded-lg transition-colors text-lg">Submit Your CV</a>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="py-20 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-brand-dark text-center mb-12">How It Works</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow border border-gray-100">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-accent/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-brand-dark mb-2">Step 1: Submit Your CV</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Share your CV with us through our simple online form. Tell us about your skills, experience, and the kind of role you are looking for.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow border border-gray-100">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-accent/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 004 0M12 5v14z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-brand-dark mb-2">Step 2: Free CV Review &amp; Prep</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Our expert team reviews your CV and provides free feedback to optimise it for your target roles. We help you highlight your strengths and stand out to employers.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow border border-gray-100">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-accent/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 10h.01M12 10h.01M16 10h.01M9 16H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2v8a2 2 0 01-2 2h-5l-5 5v-5z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-brand-dark mb-2">Step 3: Interview Coaching</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Prepare with confidence. We provide mock interviews, tailored tips, and insider knowledge about top tech employers so you walk into every interview ready to impress.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow border border-gray-100">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-accent/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 13.255A23.931 23.931 0 0112 15c-3.183 0-6.22-.62-9-1.745M16 6V4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-4a2 2 0 00-2 2v2m4 6h.01z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-brand-dark mb-2">Step 4: Placement &amp; Support</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">We match you with leading tech companies and guide you through offers and negotiations. Our support continues even after you land the role to ensure your long-term success.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="py-20 bg-brand-light">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-brand-dark text-center mb-12">Why Work With Us?</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-accent/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-brand-dark mb-2">Free CV Review</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Get professional feedback on your CV at no cost. We help you present your experience in the best possible light to attract top employers.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-accent/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 10h.01M12 10h.01M16 10h.01M9 16H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2v8a2 2 0 01-2 2h-5l-5 5v-5z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-brand-dark mb-2">Interview Preparation</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Ace your interviews with our coaching sessions. We cover your responses, body language, and technical readiness tailored to your target role.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-accent/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-brand-dark mb-2">Career Coaching</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Receive ongoing career guidance and mentorship. We help you navigate your career path, from skill development to long-term career planning.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-accent/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 13.255A23.931 23.931 0 0112 15c-3.183 0-6.22-.62-9-1.745M16 6V4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-4a2 2 0 00-2 2v2m4 6h6m2 5a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-brand-dark mb-2">Access to Exclusive Roles</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Gain access to exclusive job opportunities not advertised publicly. We connect you with leading tech companies actively seeking talent like yours.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
